OL,3,C'Our hearts are heavy': Wife of
OL,4,CSpeedway star left in coma after crash
OL,6,FThe wife of Speedway star Tai
OL,7,FWoffinden has thanked fans for their
OL,8,Fsupport after he was left in a coma
OL,9,Ffollowing a major crash.
OL,11,FWoffinden, who races with Sheffield
OL,12,FTigers, was involved in a collision
OL,13,Fwith a teammate during a race in
OL,14,FPoland on Sunday, 31 March.
OL,16,FThe 34-year-old, who is originally
OL,17,Ffrom Scunthorpe, suffered multiple
OL,18,Ffractures and a chest injury, and was
OL,19,Ftaken by helicopter to hospital where
OL,20,Fhe is in a medically induced coma on a
OL,21,Fventilator.
