OL,3,C'Our hearts are heavy': Wife of
OL,4,CSpeedway star left in coma after crash
OL,6,FHis wife, Faye, flew out from their
OL,7,Fhome in Australia on Monday to be by
OL,8,Fhis bedside.
OL,10,FIn an Instagram post she thanked fans
OL,11,Ffor their love and support.
OL,13,F"Right now, our hearts are heavy, and
OL,14,Fwe are taking things one moment at a
OL,15,Ftime," she said.
OL,17,F"Please know how deeply grateful we
OL,18,Fare for your patience, your love, and
OL,19,Fyour support - it truly means the
OL,20,Fworld to us.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
