OL,3,C'Our hearts are heavy': Wife of
OL,4,CSpeedway star left in coma after crash
OL,6,F"In the midst of this incredibly
OL,7,Fdifficult time, your support reminds
OL,8,Fus that we are not facing this alone.
OL,9,FHowever, we are still processing
OL,10,Feverything and need a little more time
OL,11,Fto understand where things stand
OL,12,Fbefore sharing any further updates. We
OL,13,Fappreciate your patience and
OL,14,Funderstanding more than we can say."
OL,16,FShe added: "We will share more when we
OL,17,Fare able. Thank you from the bottom of
OL,18,Four hearts."
