OL,3,C'Our hearts are heavy': Wife of
OL,4,CSpeedway star left in coma after crash
OL,6,FWoffinden is a three-time Grand Prix
OL,7,Fworld champion, winning in 2013, 2015,
OL,8,Fand 2018. He had recently returned to
OL,9,Fracing after a broken elbow injury in
OL,10,FJune ended his 2024 season for the
OL,11,FTigers.
OL,13,FIn a statement earlier this week,
OL,14,FSheffield Speedway, said: "We are in
OL,15,Fconstant communication with his family.
OL,17,F"Sheffield Speedway once again
OL,18,Fpolitely asks supporters not to
OL,19,Frespond to rumours out of respect to
OL,20,FTai and his family."
